      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. so if the voltage is just fluctuating, does that mean the battery is actually being damaged too? i'm worried about it dying completely while im out somewhere. is there anything else i should look for in the engine bay that might be related to these power fluctuations?",
